Package: CAseriation
Type: Package
Title: Contingency table seriation by Correspondence Analysis.
Version: 0.2
Date: 2016-09-13
Author: Gianmarco ALBERTI
Maintainer: Gianmarco ALBERTI
    <gianmarcoalberti@tin.it><gianmarco.alberti@um.edu.mt>
Description: CAseriation allows to sort the rows and columns of the input
    contingency table according to the scores of rows and columns on the
    Correspondence Analysis' dimension selected by the user. The package also allows
    to plot the CA scatterplot of selected dimensions, and to seek for clusters in
    the dataset. As for seriation, two plots are returned, displaying the sorted
    contingency table. A battleship plot for the seriated table is also provided.
    The results are also exported into tab delimited .txt files.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.1),ca,FactoMineR,seriation,plotrix,ggplot2
License: GPL2
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
